rT7Im4Kuittcun","ref":"Ps.47.7","text":"For God is the King of all the earth: sing ye praises with understanding."},{"id":"recSAWhcdkzCnYRcx","ref":"Ps.47.8","text":"God reigneth over the heathen: God sitteth upon the throne of his holiness."}]}
